questions.description:
This question will be resolved using the last value of the EURO STOXX 50 Volatility Index VSTOXX (V2TX) reported by STOXX Digital (<a href = "https://www.stoxx.com/index-details?symbol=V2TX"target="_blank">https://www.stoxx.com/index-details?symbol=V2TX</a>) for the date of interest. To access the relevant data:
- Select 'Data'; 
- Download 'Historical Data’; 
- Refer to the ‘Indexvalue’ column for the date of interest.
Question will be closed the day before the date of interest.
